%N A015439 Inverse of 1430th cyclotomic polynomial.
%C A015439 Periodic with period length 1430. - _Ray Chandler_, Apr 07 2017
%H A015439 Ray Chandler, <a href="/A015439/b015439.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..2000</a>
%H A015439 <a href="/index/Per#periodic">Index entries for periodic sequences</a>, period 1430.
